---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const basePath = base.endsWith("/") ? base : `${base}/`;
---

<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>About | Rodrigo Santos Tech</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chakra+Petch:wght@500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #07101d;
        --line: rgba(116, 160, 224, 0.34);
        --ink: #ecf4ff;
        --muted: #a4bada;
        --accent: #36d2ff;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "IBM Plex Sans", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        color: var(--ink);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 10% 8%, rgba(54, 210, 255, 0.18) 0%, transparent 32%),
          linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(9, 28, 48, 0.96) 0%, rgba(4, 11, 19, 1) 55%, rgba(7, 16, 29, 1) 100%),
          var(--bg);
      }

      main {
        width: min(760px, 92vw);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2.8rem 0 4rem;
      }

      .shell {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: rgba(10, 24, 42, 0.86);
        padding: 1.8rem;
      }

      .profile {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 170px 1fr;
        gap: 1.2rem;
        align-items: center;
        margin: 1rem 0 1.2rem;
      }

      .avatar {
        width: 170px;
        aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        object-fit: cover;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 26px rgba(4, 13, 25, 0.45);
      }

      .profile-text {
        color: #d8e6f8;
      }

      .label {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
      }

      .name {
        margin: 0.25rem 0 0.65rem;
        font-family: "Chakra Petch", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.7rem);
      }

      .linkedin {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.45rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      h1 {
        font-family: "Chakra Petch", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4.5vw, 2.8rem);
      }

      p {
        color: #d8e6f8;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      .home {
        display: inline-flex;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        .profile {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          justify-items: center;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="shell">
        <h1>About</h1>
        <div class="profile">
          <img
            class="avatar"
            src={`${basePath}profile-rodrigo.jpg`}
            alt="Foto de Rodrigo Santos"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="profile-text">
            <p class="label">Perfil</p>
            <p class="name">Rodrigo Silva Santos</p>
            <a
              class="linkedin"
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rodrigosilvacs/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noreferrer noopener"
            >
              LinkedIn / rodrigosilvacs
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p>
          Sou engenheiro de software focado em confiabilidade, arquitetura orientada a domínio e experiência de desenvolvimento.
        </p>
        <p>
          Este espaço documenta decisões que funcionaram, falhas que ensinaram caro e trade-offs reais de produção.
        </p>
        <a class="home" href={basePath}>Voltar para início</a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
